  "system": {
    "description": "<p><strong>In a way, we are magicians. We are alchemists, sorcerers and wizards. We are a very strange bunch. But there is great fun in being a wizard.</strong></p><p><em>— Billy Joel</em></p><p>Students of the arcane arts, researchers and developers of spells as academic pursuit.</p><h3>Iconic Wizards</h3><ul><li><strong>Harry Dresden</strong>, <em>The Dresden Files</em></li><li><strong>Merlyn</strong>, <em>Arthurian legend</em></li><li><strong>Sparrow</strong>, <em>Earthsea series</em></li><li><strong>Sypha Belnades</strong>, <em>Castlevania</em></li></ul><h3>Playing Wizard</h3><p>The wizard is a squishy blaster focused on Casting Spells. Stay in safety to Cast your Spells and discover Enemy weaknesses.</p><p><strong>Action:</strong> Cast<br /><strong>Move:</strong> Backline<br /><strong>Starting Perk:</strong> Astronomer or Mage<br /><strong>Key Stat:</strong> Reason<br /><strong>Complexity:</strong> ★★★★☆</p><h3>Training</h3><p><strong>Weapons —</strong><br /><strong>Skills:</strong> Arcana, and 4 others</p><p></p><h3><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Class Features</span></h3><table class=\"NormalTable\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:9pt\">Level</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:9pt\">Features</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"82\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:9pt\">Mana</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:9pt\">Spells</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">1st</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Spellcaster, Page Master</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"82\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">4</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">4</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">2nd</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Sculpt Spell</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"82\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">8</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">4</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">3rd</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Perk</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"82\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">12</span