        "description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You can Cast Spells using Arcana.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Spells:</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You learn 4 Spells. You learn 1 other Spell every 2 Wizard Levels hereafter.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Mana:</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Your Maximum Mana is equal to (4 × your Wizard Level), and the highest amount of Mana you can spend to Cast a Spell is equal to (Reason + half your Wizard Level, round up). You regain spent Mana when you Rest or Study.</span> </p>",
